00:36:15.440 --> 00:36:16.840
- Please.
- She has to die.

480
00:36:17.008 --> 00:36:18.840
Because you have to be punished.

481
00:36:19.010 --> 00:36:20.501
You slept with Joe's wife.

482
00:36:20.679 --> 00:36:23.046
And between you and
me. I don't take that lightly.

483
00:36:23.214 --> 00:36:25.513
- Get off me.
- Let her go. That's not Joe's wife.

484
00:36:25.684 --> 00:36:27.516
It's a freaking metaphor. Ryan.

485
00:36:31.222 --> 00:36:35.421
- Tell them to stay back.
- Back. back. Stay back. Stay back.

486
00:36:35.593 --> 00:36:37.186
Okay.

487
00:36:38.329 --> 00:36:42.733
Now you gotta let
her go. Hey. kill me.

488
00:36:43.401 --> 00:36:45.870
No. I have to kill her.

489
00:36:46.037 --> 00:36:48.563
Love hurts. Ryan.
That's the theme here.

490
00:36:48.740 --> 00:36:51.335
Joe Carroll gets a happy
ending. You don't get one.

491
00:36:51.509 --> 00:36:54.775
Cheaters don't get happy
endings. My husband didn't get one.

492
00:36:54.979 --> 00:36:56.277
You're right.

493
00:36:56.481 --> 00:36:57.881
It was a mistake.

494
00:36:58.049 --> 00:37:00.109
I shouldn't have done it.

495
00:37:00.885 --> 00:37:03.377
- Then why did you?
- Please. please. just let her go.

496
00:37:03.555 --> 00:37:05.990
Why? Why did you do it?

497
00:37:11.362 --> 00:37:13.126
Because I love her.

498
00:37:16.134 --> 00:37:18.000
Thank you.

499
00:37:18.636 --> 00:37:20.571
That was very honest.

500
00:37:20.739 --> 00:37:21.763
And now...

501
00:37:23.308 --> 00:37:25.504
you gotta do something for me.

502
00:37:26.077 --> 00:37:27.807
Because you're right.

503
00:37:28.913 --> 00:37:32.577
I do. I need to be punished.

504
00:37:34.953 --> 00:37:36.319
Come on. just kill me.

505
00:37:36.521 --> 00:37:38.717
- Stay back. RYAN:
Because I still love her.

506
00:37:39.758 --> 00:37:42.557
And I can't un-love her.

507
00:37:43.595 --> 00:37:50.024
And the only way that you and Joe are
gonna get a happy ending is if you kill me.

508
00:37:51.636 --> 00:37:52.899
So come on. just do it.

509
00:37:53.671 --> 00:37:55.230
Just...

510
00:37:56.141 --> 00:37:58.303
take that nail gun...

511
00:37:58.676 --> 00:38:01.407
shoot me right in the
head. You can do it.

512
00:38:02.113 --> 00:38:04.275
Come on. I know you can.

513
00:38:04.449 --> 00:38:06.350
Do it now.

514
00:38:06.818 --> 00:38:08.844
Now. Now!

515
00:38:11.956 --> 00:38:15.358
No. no!

516
00:38:27.305 --> 00:38:30.639
Ryan Hardy is proving to be
more of a challenge than I thought.

517
00:38:30.809 --> 00:38:35.144
Yeah. I wouldn't underestimate
that man. I made that mistake once.

518
00:38:36.848 --> 00:38:38.612
What happened?

519
00:38:39.617 --> 00:38:42.382
- Louise is dead.
- Oh.

520
00:38:42.554 --> 00:38:44.716
Amanda is in federal custody.

521
00:38:44.889 --> 00:38:46.721
That is unfortunate.

522
00:38:47.325 --> 00:38:49.351
I'm sorry about Louise.

523
00:38:49.527 --> 00:38:52.087
I know she was important to you.

524
00:38:54.599 --> 00:38:55.623
Not really.

525
00:38:57.535 --> 00:39:00.198
Maybe. heh. I don't know. heh.

526
00:39:00.371 --> 00:39:01.964
There is good news.

527
00:39:02.140 --> 00:39:05.804
At noon today FBI Agent Nick Donovan
made an encrypted cell phone call...

528
00:39:05.977 --> 00:39:09.243
to Quantico. Virginia checking
the status of Claire Matthews.

529
00:39:09.414 --> 00:39:11.144
We deciphered that encryption.

530
00:39:11.883 --> 00:39:13.749
And what did you find?

531
00:39:13.918 --> 00:39:16.251
Uh. call was transferred
to several Bureau offices...

532
00:39:16.421 --> 00:39:19.914
before it was finally transferred
to U.S. Marshall Scott Turner.

533
00:39:20.124 --> 00:39:23.060
Currently in charge of
personal security for Claire.

534
00:39:23.228 --> 00:39:26.858
We were able to narrow her location
to the nearest cell phone tower.

535
00:39:27.565 --> 00:39:31.696
Your wife is in Huntingdon
County. Pennsylvania.

536
00:39:33.638 --> 00:39:39.168
Oh. that is excellent
work. my friend.

537
00:39:41.045 --> 00:39:43.105
I wanna interview Amanda
first thing in the morning.

538
00:39:43.281 --> 00:39:46.012
- Donovan said that wouldn't happen.
- We can break her.

539
00:39:46.184 --> 00:39:49.677
The thing about Joe's cult members
is they don't come to this party sane.

540
00:39:49.854 --> 00:39:52.847
- You just gotta speak their language.
- Look. I agree with you.

541
00:39:53.024 --> 00:39:55.926
But Director Franklin ordered
that she be transferred to D.C.

542
00:39:56.094 --> 00:39:59.553
- They're questioning her at headquarters.
- Ah. You're kidding me.

543
00:40:00.431 --> 00:40:03.526
They're moving the investigation
there. They're taking the lead.

544
00:40:03.701 --> 00:40:05.465
How do you feel about that?

545
00:40:06.571 --> 00:40:08.301
Like a failure.

546
00:40:12.911 --> 00:40:15.312
Hey. you're not.

547
00:40:20.318 --> 00:40:23.413
So all that stuff Ryan was saying
tonight about Claire Matthews.

548
00:40:25.390 --> 00:40:26.722
He's still hung up on her.

549
00:40:27.458 --> 00:40:28.756
He loves her.

550
00:40:30.194 --> 00:40:31.594
That's just twisted.

551
00:41:19.243 --> 00:41:21.508
Were you expecting someone else?

552
00:41:22.613 --> 00:41:25.173
- Joe. maybe?
- What is it?

553
00:41:25.350 --> 00:41:28.752
Well. Joe's a little busy right now.
but. uh. I've been looking for you.

554
00:41:29.554 --> 00:41:33.252
And you found me.
What is it I can do for you?

555
00:41:34.492 --> 00:41:37.656
Earlier I received a
very exciting e-mail.

556
00:41:38.162 --> 00:41:43.123
I wanted to tell you about it.
but I thought I'd surprise you.

557
00:41:47.338 --> 00:41:48.966
So follow me.

558
00:42:10.528 --> 00:42:12.588
Hello. Emma.
